Hello Michelle and Grant,
&nbsp;
Thank you for reaching out with your query.
&nbsp;
Regarding the Media mail option not being available, please allow us some time to check this case. We will update you soon.
&nbsp;
Regarding address verification on checkout, please note that the plugin will return the rates on checkout based on the address provided.
Address verification on checkout is not a functionality of the plugin.
&nbsp;
You can use another plugin which provides this functionality on checkout on your store.
&nbsp;
Let us know if you have any queries in the meantime.
&nbsp;
Thanks and Regards,
Touseef
Team PluginHive

Hello Michelle Alfandari,
&nbsp;
Thank you for your response.
&nbsp;
I understand your concern.
&nbsp;
However, we do not have any solution for address verification on checkout.
&nbsp;
Let us know if you have any queries in the meantime.
&nbsp;
Thanks and Regards,
Touseef
Team PluginHive

Hello Michelle,
&nbsp;
Sorry for the difficulties you faced in generating shipping labels.
&nbsp;
Please allow us some time we check and get back to you with an update.
&nbsp;
In the meantime can you please try to cross check the error once with USPS team? and verify everythign was set correctly at your account level like payment?
&nbsp;
Do let us know how it goes.
&nbsp;
Thanks and Regards,
Manohar V
Team PluginHive

